Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.82,main,Miyako,0,0,0,,Ah... C-Chờ chút đã nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:48.81,main,Hinata,0,0,0,,Sao vậy?
